OL,3,CEnd of an era for Merthyr Tydfil as
OL,4,CHoover say they're leaving for good
OL,6,FHoover has announced it is withdrawing
OL,7,Fits last operations from Merthyr
OL,8,FTydfil, marking the end of an era for
OL,9,Fthe town.
OL,11,FHundreds of jobs were lost when the
OL,12,Fwashing machine factory closed its
OL,13,Fdoors in 2009 after 61 years, with
OL,14,Fpart of the iconic site still used for
OL,15,Fdistribution.
OL,17,FHowever, now Hoover owners Haier have
OL,18,Fannounced they are pulling its
OL,19,Fworkforce from the town completely.
