OL,3,CEnd of an era for Merthyr Tydfil as
OL,4,CHoover say they're leaving for good
OL,6,FAt one point, the Hoover factory was
OL,7,Fone of the largest employers in Wales,
OL,8,Femploying as many as 5,000 staff in
OL,9,Fthe 1970s.
OL,11,FThe complete withdrawal of the company
OL,12,Ffrom the town has been described as an
OL,13,F"end of an era".
OL,15,FIn a letter to Gerald Jones MP and
OL,16,FDawn Bowden MS, the huge firm
OL,17,Fconfirmed it announced the plans at
OL,18,Fthe start of May 2024 and 45 warehouse
OL,19,Fjobs would be lost at the site.
