OL,3,CEnd of an era for Merthyr Tydfil as
OL,4,CHoover say they're leaving for good
OL,6,FThey said they are selling their
OL,7,Ffinished goods national distribution
OL,8,Fcentre and that it will close over the
OL,9,Fnext 12 to 18 months.
OL,11,FThe remaining staff at the site will
OL,12,Fbe offered to transfer to the
OL,13,Fcompany's site in Rugby, Warwickshire,
OL,14,Fwith owners saying they will be
OL,15,Fexploring other opportunities for
OL,16,Fstaff. They acknowledged that the
OL,17,Fdecision "was not made lightly,
OL,18,Fparticularly given Hoover's long term
OL,19,Fconnection with Merthyr".
