OL,3,CEnd of an era for Merthyr Tydfil as
OL,4,CHoover say they're leaving for good
OL,6,FThe letter read: "Last week we
OL,7,Fannounced the difficult decision that
OL,8,Fwe are close to selling our finished
OL,9,Fgoods national distribution centre
OL,10,Flocated in Merthyr Tydfil.
OL,12,F"This decision was not made lightly,
OL,13,Fparticularly given Hoover's long term
OL,14,Fconnection with Merthyr. However,
OL,15,Feconomic realities have now
OL,16,Fnecessitated a comprehensive review of
OL,17,Fmarket conditions and our operations.
OL,19,F"A final agreement to sell the land
OL,20,Fand leave the site is unlikely to be
OL,21,Fcompleted for between 12 and 18 months.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/11
