OL,3,CEnd of an era for Merthyr Tydfil as
OL,4,CHoover say they're leaving for good
OL,6,F"We are proposing that in the future
OL,7,Fwe will be outsourcing our warehouse
OL,8,Foperations to third party provider GXO
OL,9,FLogistics UK & Ireland, at a
OL,10,Fdistribution centre in the Rugby area.
OL,12,F"At Hoover, the wellbeing of our
OL,13,Fcolleagues and the success of our
OL,14,Fbusiness are top priorities. We
OL,15,Funderstand the uncertainty this
OL,16,Fdecision will create for our 45
OL,17,Fwarehouse colleagues and the local
OL,18,Fcommunity and we are committed to
OL,19,Fmanaging this transition with the
OL,20,Futmost care and consideration."
