OL,3,CEnd of an era for Merthyr Tydfil as
OL,4,CHoover say they're leaving for good
OL,6,FOwners said their priority now would
OL,7,Fbe to support affected colleagues and
OL,8,Fthose who do choose to transfer to
OL,9,FRugby will have their continuous
OL,10,Fservice protected.
OL,12,FIt continued: "Our primary focus now
OL,13,Fis supporting affected colleagues
OL,14,Fthrough this transition. Colleagues
OL,15,Fwho are primarily involved in
OL,16,Fwarehouse operations will have the
OL,17,Fopportunity to transfer to Rugby and
OL,18,Fwill have their continuous employment
OL,19,Fand contractual rights protected.
