OL,3,CEnd of an era for Merthyr Tydfil as
OL,4,CHoover say they're leaving for good
OL,6,F"In addition to the opportunities at
OL,7,FRugby, we will explore any other
OL,8,Favailable alternative employment
OL,9,Fopportunities within Hoover for our
OL,10,Fwarehouse operations colleagues.
OL,12,F"We are committed to providing as much
OL,13,Fsupport as possible to our colleagues
OL,14,Fduring the consultation period and
OL,15,Fover the next 12 to 18-month proposed
OL,16,Fclosure programme.
