OL,3,CEnd of an era for Merthyr Tydfil as
OL,4,CHoover say they're leaving for good
OL,6,F"We are sorry to be ending our long-
OL,7,Fheld presence in Merthyr Tydfil which
OL,8,Fhas played such an important part of
OL,9,Fthe brand's development and will
OL,10,Falways remain a significant part of
OL,11,FHoover's history."
OL,13,FBy 1995 Hoover was sold to the Candy
OL,14,FGroup, which invested #40million in
OL,15,Ftheir plants in Merthyr and
OL,16,FCambuslang, Scotland, making it the
OL,17,Ffourth largest producer of washing
OL,19,Fmachines, refrigerators and similar
OL,20,Fproducts in Europe. Hoover was
OL,21,Facquired by Haier in 2019.
