OL,3,CEnd of an era for Merthyr Tydfil as
OL,4,CHoover say they're leaving for good
OL,6,FGerald Jones MP shared the letter on
OL,7,Fsocial media, adding: "This is the end
OL,8,Fof an era: Hoover's plan to leave
OL,9,FMerthyr Tydfil. It's incredibly sad
OL,10,Fthat the 45 remaining jobs will leave
OL,11,Fthe town, and I'm working with trade
OL,12,Funions to ensure staff are supported
OL,13,Fthrough this time of change."
OL,15,FDawn Bowden MS said: "Our immediate
OL,16,Ffocus is supporting affected staff
OL,17,Fthrough this time of change."
