OL,4,CHoover say they're leaving for good
OL,6,FMerthyr Tydfil Council Leader, Cllr
OL,7,FGeraint Thomas, said: "The news of the
OL,8,Fclosure of the Hoover site in Merthyr
OL,9,FTydfil signifies the end of an era for
OL,10,Four town.
OL,12,F"The firm has employed thousands of
OL,13,Four residents over the years and
OL,14,Fbrought with it much needed industry
OL,15,Fafter the Second World War.
